history.content:
Are you an innovative builder working on an idea, side project, or company from your dorm room? Join Free Ventures’ Spring 2021 batch! You’ll be part of a network of successful founders and mentors to fast-track your startup’s path to success.

Free Ventures is UC Berkeley's leading pre-seed startup accelerator, crafting highly individualized paths for founders across industries and academic backgrounds in a semester-long program. Our 60+ alumni companies have tackled exciting problems in education, food tech, hardware, healthcare, and more, and have gone on to raise over $55 million from Y Combinator, Kleiner Perkins, Greylock, Accel, and 8VC.

If you are currently enrolled at UC Berkeley and working on a product or service, we encourage you to meet us and apply to the next Free Ventures batch!

Infosession: Meet our team and a past FreeV founder who raised $500K: https://fb.me/e/44UztjgbA

Learn More: To learn more about Free Ventures and our portfolio, check out our website: www.freeventures.org/ 

Apply: Spring 2021 batch app: tinyurl.com/freev-apply-s21.

Applications are due on Friday 2/5 at midnight PST. We can’t wait to read yours!
history.subject: Free Ventures Startup Accelerator is Recruiting!
